author: Mary Kay Cabot, cleveland.com
title: Deshaun Watson piles on with the Browns jokes, joining Myles Garrett in begging Cowboys to trade up for him
text: Deshaun Watson followed in the footsteps of Myles Garrett and implored the Cowboys to trade up to No. 1 with the Browns and draft him. And he's not even from Texas.
